<h4>Rewards After Surviving Blood Moon</h4>
<p>After each survived blood moon, you receive one of the following rewards (random):</p>
<ul>
  <li>Mining Speed <strong>+10%</strong></li>
  <li>Attack damage <strong>+1</strong></li>
  <li>Thirst drain <strong>-10%</strong></li>
  <li>Hunger drain <strong>-10%</strong></li>
</ul>
<div class="tip-card">💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> Blood moon rewards stack! 6 survived blood moons = 6 bonuses. It's worth surviving every blood moon for permanent stat boosts.</div>

