<div data-lang="en" id="fog-event">
<div class="collapsible"><div class="collapsible-toggle" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="true"><h3>Fog Event</h3><span class="toggle-icon">▶</span></div><div class="collapsible-body open"><div class="collapsible-body-inner">
<p>Approximately every <strong>50 days</strong>, a fog event can occur that lasts <strong>48–72 hours</strong>. The fog drastically reduces visibility.</p>
<div class="warning-box">☁️ <strong>Important:</strong> During a fog event, mobs <em>do not burn in daylight</em>! Zombies and skeletons remain dangerous during the day. Stay at your base or reinforce your defenses!</div>
<p>If a Blood Moon coincides with a fog event — the best strategy is to wait it out safely inside your base.</p>
</div></div></div>
